Titolo: The Big Red Adventure

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: The Big Red Adventure is an adventure game developed by Dynabyte and published by Core Design for DOS in 1995. It was released for the Amiga computers in 1997 by Power Computing on CD-ROM.The Big Red Adventure is a sequel to Dynabyte's Nippon Safes Inc., a title that had been "a moderate hit all around Europe", according to Hardcore Gaming 101. It was developed in Italy.

